    parentName: "div"
  }, "Image by Mohamed Hassan from Pixabay")), mdx("p", null, "Mentoring is a process of informal knowledge transfer. The one who passes on the knowledge is called a mentor, and the one who receives it is usually called a prot\xE9g\xE9 (but I\u2019ve also seen the term mentee). The mentor usually meets his prot\xE9g\xE9 in person and gives his valuable advice in a friendly atmosphere. Often a friendly relationship is established between the mentor and his prot\xE9g\xE9, and mentoring often includes mental support to help the prot\xE9g\xE9 overcome his obstacles."), mdx("p", null, "About two weeks ago, at a meeting of our public speaking club ", mdx("a", _extends({
